{"tid":121723,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"求大家介紹好用嘅化妝品俾我","createTime":"2017-02-15T12:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T10:39:09.000Z","uid":29813,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"683439fc5d13abb1338d915cfe4217cca6204274","tid":121723,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:44:59.000Z","msg":"我化咗妝差唔多有兩年<br />\n但我啲化妝品一直都未買齊<br />\n得base foundation eyeliner  mascara 同唇膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲化妝品唔係話好好用 成日化到成個粉樣咁<br />\n出街見到啲人化得好靚 好自然 好通透<br />\n有種想衝上前問佢用咗咩化妝品嘅衝動<br />\n其實自己都有喺YouTube睇人化妝<br />\n見佢哋成日推介話呢隻好用嗰隻好用 <br />\n但係又驚佢哋好似大佬B咁 <br />\n收咗錢就乜嘢狗屎垃圾都sale<br />\n所以希望係連登得到大家嘅睇法<br />\n希望大家可以推介一啲化妝品俾我參考下<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3216bfe59f94e9a280dc1556e5c2d3c53c1529","tid":121723,"uid":76765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:46:31.000Z","msg":"3ce"},{"pid":"28aede34bbabadec4426b3d7ba113892c4ebed4f","tid":121723,"uid":71742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:49:35.000Z","msg":"Sofina long keep base"},{"pid":"bd69b7ccce8d72e6405e1e5b3907d8a92d2300dc","tid":121723,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:52:12.000Z","msg":"我用緊3ce隻粉底筆<br />\n同埋隻base正正就係Sofina long keep base<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8efe8efada70be8c85dde77c9cb99e9046b0f0c3","tid":121723,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:53:09.000Z","msg":"Kiko Milano <