><br />\n前者L'Or&eacute;al group ga <br />\n買three la"},{"pid":"3ee3d2b80b57d097f881674dbc17eac64f9952cd","tid":121723,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T13:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想唔粉樣去12蚊店/sasa買啲化妝海綿<br />\n搽好晒skin care同base<br />\n用化妝海綿輕輕逐少逐少咁印上粉底液<br />\n唔好「抹」落塊臉度就唔會變粉樣</blockquote><br />\n有咁做<br />\n其實我諗我嘅問題係我唔識上碎粉（啱啱先發現上面打留咗碎粉）<br />\n可能係因為我冇買大嘅掃 同埋盒碎粉唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人用過Soap and glory one heck of a blot<br />\n想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e3aa183cedb3484c8766f3804dad83a9f5cfea","tid":121723,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T13:06:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想買新嘅foundation <br />\n但唔知買Giorgio Armani定three嘅好<br />\n聽講兩隻都好好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n前者L'Or&eacute;al group ga <br />\n買three la</blockquote><br />\n絲打有冇用過？<br />\n我都係偏向想買three 但知道佢遮瑕力比較低<br />\n所以苦惱緊買邊隻遮瑕産品去補足"},{"pid":"bf9afa576c1abbd4932209a48cdae9cd5251bcd9","tid":121723,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T13:07:57.000Z","msg":"你要平定貴啊 <br />\n唇膏cdp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過都貴既<br />\n粉餅 用緊canmake 個圓金蓋棉花糖系列 <br />\nMascara就dollywink<br />\n胭脂就用得豪宅乜都用下<br />\n你可以買冇咁上色既 手耐都唔怕 例如Clinique  pansy pop好岩白皮用<br />\nEyeliner:love liner<br />\n另外addiction既眼影都好靚 又唔貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d7f13a8fcd74f757340a1e22a61b753decfa75","tid":121723,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T13:09:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想買新嘅foundation <br />\n但唔知買Giorgio Armani定three嘅好<br />\n聽講兩隻都好好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n前者L'Or&eacute;al group ga <br />\n買three la</blockquote><br />\n絲打有冇用過？<br />\n我都係偏向想買three 但知道佢遮瑕力比較低<br />\n所以苦惱緊買邊隻遮瑕産品去補足</blockquote><br />\n冇唔 唔用粉底液 多數用完base再局部遮 上碎粉 <br />\n最近懶到base-&gt;碎粉 完 <br />\n黑眼圈都費事理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce106114715c6efea6707d1a197e46e3d14eead","tid":121723,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T13:10:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你要平定貴啊 <br />\n唇膏cdp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過都貴既<br />\n粉餅 用緊canmake 個圓金蓋棉花糖系列 <br />\nMascara就dollywink<br />\n胭脂就用得好雜 乜都用下<br />\n你可以買冇咁上色既 手殘都唔怕 例如Clinique  pansy pop好岩白皮用<br />\nEyeliner:love liner<br />\n另外addiction既眼影都好靚 又唔貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打錯好多字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4cefcad84affe809dbba9989962e8c3fcb7ed7","tid":121723,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T13:10:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你要平定貴啊 <br />\n唇膏cdp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過都貴既<br />\n粉餅 用緊canmake 個圓金蓋棉花糖系列 <br />\nMascara就dollywink<br />\n胭脂就用得豪宅乜都用下<br />\n你可以買冇咁上色既 手耐都唔怕 例如Clinique  pansy pop好岩白皮用<br />\nEyeliner:love liner<br />\n另外addiction既眼影都好靚 又唔貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平同貴都無所謂 只要好用就得<br />\n多謝絲打介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865c67a66d27e51063e300ab1dcb9c91a2f4c4d3","tid":121723,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T13:11:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想買新嘅foundation <br />\n但